OL,3,CDonald Campbell's hydroplane runs
OL,4,Cagain but now needs 'few more
OL,5,Cadjustments'
OL,7,FDonald Campbell's legendary
OL,8,Fhydroplane, the Bluebird K7, has run
OL,9,Fagain today on Coniston Water.
OL,11,FThe craft spent about six minutes
OL,12,Fbeing propelled by its own steam this
OL,13,Fmorning (Thursday, May 14), before
OL,14,Fpilot Dave Warby turned the engine off.
OL,16,FAn announcement was made at Coniston,
OL,17,Fsaying: "It obviously needs some extra
OL,18,Fadjustment. The engineers thought they
OL,19,Fhad done enough, but obviously a
OL,20,Flittle more is required.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
