CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779185247
OL,3,CDonald Campbell's hydroplane runs
OL,4,Cagain but now needs 'few more
OL,5,Cadjustments'
OL,7,F"She's very nearly there. It's not
OL,8,Fsomething you can do with a Swiss army
OL,9,Fknife."
OL,11,FHopes are still high, however, as the
OL,12,Fweather is expected to stay suitable
OL,13,Ffor further runs.
OL,15,FIt is also planned that Sir Malcom
OL,16,FCampbell's Bluebird K3, which broke
OL,17,Frecords before son Donald Campbell
OL,18,Fdid, will go out on Coniston Water
OL,19,Ftoday.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
